# An Enhanced tool to process PDB structures based on Gemmi

# Install
```commandline

conda install python=3.12.12 anarci hmmer dockq trimesh rtree pdbfixer dssp -c bioconda -c conda-forge
pip install gemmi_protools
```

# Usage

## read structures
```commandline
from gemmi_protools import StructureParser

# load structure
st=StructureParser()
st.load_from_file("7mmo.cif")

# get chain IDs
print(st.chain_ids)
```
